item.title: Hello World
item.description: I can no longer remember how many times I’ve created this very same file due to various errors and deployment failures. But, I love debugging! Coming from a field where subjectivity defines the output, I’m in love with coding that always has some form of solution. With that, this shall be my first ‘final’ post.
